title: Ga Tech beats Florida State on 78-yard return on final play
text:
> Florida Ga Tech beats Florida State on 78-yard return on final play Florida State punter Cason Beatty (38) walks off the field after the second half of an NCAA college football game against Georgia Tech, Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, in Atlanta. Georgia Tech won 22-16. (AP Photo/Mike Stewart) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
